---
layout: base
nav: journal
ogType: article
---
<main class="wrap">
  <article class="prose">
    {% if cover %}<img class="post-cover" src="{{ cover }}" alt="" data-reveal="0" />{% endif %}
    <header class="post-head" data-reveal="0">
      <time datetime="{{ page.date | htmlDate }}">{{ page.date | readableDate }}</time>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span>{{ content | readingTime }}</span>
        {% if tags and tags.length %}<span class="dot">·</span><span>{{ tags | join(", ") }}</span>{% endif %}
      </div>
      <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
    </header>

    <div data-reveal="1">
      {% if lede %}<p class="lede" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">{{ lede }}</p>{% endif %}
      {{ content | safe }}
    </div>

    {% set newer = collections.posts | getNextCollectionItem %}
    {% set older = collections.posts | getPreviousCollectionItem %}
    {% if newer or older %}
    <nav class="post-nav" aria-label="More writing" data-reveal="2">
      {% if newer %}
      <a class="prev" href="{{ newer.url }}">
        <span>← newer</span>
        <strong>{{ newer.data.title }}</strong>
      </a>
      {% endif %}
      {% if older %}
      <a class="next" href="{{ older.url }}">
        <span>older →</span>
        <strong>{{ older.data.title }}</strong>
      </a>
      {% endif %}
    </nav>
    {% endif %}

    <a href="/journal/" class="back">back to journal</a>
  </article>
</main>
